title: history of Indian Philosophy
description:
CAMBRIDGE UNIVERSITY PRESS   HISTORY OF INDIAN PHILOSOPHY 1952-1961




    Football came to earth in england , but philosophy did so in at least 

    two places: Greece and India , being this last one the classic GAP in european

    humanities.



    This set is the result of 30 years of work by the author , but have in mind 

    that the physical death of Mr. Dasgupta  in 1952 left somehow incomplete the 

    last book of the collection (kashmir schools).
